                    <h2>Process</h2>
                    <h4>Understanding the problem</h4>                    
                    <p>	Mergers & acquisitions have made for a disparity of systems. The current state for DXC leadership requires navigating among 30+ different application across 7 different business functions to perform and to keep track of requests.</p><p>Each system has unique loginâ€™s, security requirements, notification settings, and processes. This has caused endless delays and confusion across all business functions.</p>
