                    <h4>Took initiative to talk to users</h4>
                    <p>In the initial kickoff meeting with the steakholders, I requested access to a few users to interview. I collaborated with the business analyst on the team to develop and facilitate a test plan. Together we formalize interview questions, scheduled and ran interviews, systhesized the data, and presented the findings to the team.</p>
